{{Infobox brain|Name=直回|Latin=gyrus rectus|Image=Gray729 straight gyrus.png|Caption=左侧额叶底部（直回位于橙色标记处）|Image2=Human brainstem anterior view 2 description.JPG|Caption2=人脑底部（直回位于数字1标记处）|IsPartOf=|Components=|Artery=|Vein=}}'''直回'''（英文：Straight gyrus）是[[大脑|大脑]][[额叶|额叶]]底部的一个[[脑回|脑回]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Gyrus rectus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/gyrus-rectus?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-11|last=Maingard|first=Julian|work=|publisher=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422065149/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/gyrus-rectus?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Straight gyrus|url=http://braininfo.org/centraldirectory.aspx?ID=94|accessdate=2021-04-11|work=|publisher=BrainInfo|archive-date=2021-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412002739/http://braininfo.org/centraldirectory.aspx?ID=94|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=直回|url=https://www.imaios.com/cn/e-Anatomy/node_322323/2772|accessdate=2021-04-11|work=IMAIOS|language=zh}}</ref>。直回一侧紧靠[[中央縱裂|中央纵裂]]、经[[大脑半球|大脑半球]]内侧延伸至[[额上回|额上回]]，另一侧与[[眶回|眶回]]相隔、中间有[[嗅沟|嗅沟]]隔开<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Orbital Gyri - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/orbital-gyri|accessdate=2021-04-11|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411181723/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/orbital-gyri|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 功能 ==
直回的功能尚不清楚，但可能与高阶认知功能有关<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Relationship between Gyrus Rectus Resection and Cognitive Impairment after Surgery for Ruptured Anterior Communicating Artery Aneurysms|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5104846/|last=Joo|first=Myung Sung|last2=Park|first2=Dong Sun|date=2016-9|journal=Journal of Cerebrovascular and Endovascular Neurosurgery|issue=3|doi=10.7461/jcen.2016.18.3.223|volume=18|pages=223–228|issn=2234-8565|pmc=5104846|pmid=27847765|last3=Moon|first3=Chang Taek|last4=Chun|first4=Young Il|last5=Song|first5=Sang Woo|last6=Roh|first6=Hong Gee}}</ref>。

